articles.title: Sania Mirza bids farewell to Australian Open after defeat in mixed doubles quarter-finals - India Today
articles.description: Australian Open: Sania Mirza, who had earlier said that the 2022 season will be the last of her career, and her American partner Rajeev Ram lost 4-6, 6-7 (5-7) to Australian pair Jason Kubler and Jaimee Fourlis in the mixed doubles quarter-final.
